Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:27.15,op_english (insert song),,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Keep having their way with me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:30.89,op_english (insert song),,0000,0000,0000,,All the time I have to live
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:33.88,op_english (insert song),,0000,0000,0000,,Warping where my dreams will go
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:39.29,op_english (insert song),,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Even though they're so important to me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:43.05,op_english (insert song),,0000,0000,0000,,If it's all I can, right now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:45.85,op_english (insert song),,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go eat something sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:48.67,op_english (insert song),,0000,0000,0000,,Stop thinking like that
