Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:58.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:00.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your dorms!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:02.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! We have to watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:04.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Why don't you just go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:06.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:11.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:14.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me more energy, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:18.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no one can do that for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do it with our own strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:24.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:26.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeyama{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:30.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently running a high speed password{\fnNyala}-{\fn}cracking program.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:31.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be done soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:34.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, please call me Christ.{FOTC: And call me Christ.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:37.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:39.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Takeyama{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:40.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Copy all the data!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:42.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That would take too much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:44.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An hour, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:46.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And please, call me Chri—{FOTC: And call me Christ.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:47.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we just take the whole hard disk? {check}{ハードデイスクごと引っこ抜くか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:48.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll notice that!{ばれるじゃない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:49.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:52.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just show us any suspicious data, Takeyama{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:53.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A list of students?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:00.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,NPCs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:03.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're included too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:05.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a name register!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not going to be anything suspicious there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This really is just trespassing!{FOTC: "is just"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:09.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The diversionary squad has been suppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:14.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel is returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:17.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't manage to get anything this time either...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:22.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, stop screwing with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:27.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Their music supports us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:34.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:36.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just being lenient till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:37.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky!{今までは多めに見てやってただけだ。図に乗るな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:42.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're confiscating all these instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:44.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the cultural festival or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:46.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you get away with this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can throw this away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:52.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:59.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!{止めんか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:10.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:26.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it over.
