Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The new song...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:21.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeyama{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:24.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. And call me Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:27.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:31.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To go on singing like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:37.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I was saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:40.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save someone else like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:41.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:46.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:01.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iwasawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:15.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you summarize what we learned, Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:21.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel is developing her own powers herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:26.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And strangely enough, it looks like she's doing it the same way we make weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:28.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:31.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not certain yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:33.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I won't say anything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:36.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't be so secretive, Yurippe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:41.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that she needs to use the same methods as us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:43.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The only conclusion we can draw from that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:44.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the worst case scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:48.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no gods anywhere.{FOTC: What should we do?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:52.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't Angel get her powers from God?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:55.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she have to develop them herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:58.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring up the next issue then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:05.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Iwasawa{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:06.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Angel erase her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:07.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was in the middle of a concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:09.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying happened, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:11.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could have done that to Iwasawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:13.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:16.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She accepted it herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:18.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.95,0:22:25.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To disappear, you have to obey what Angel says and lead a normal student life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:28.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But that isn't the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.07,0:24:17.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.57,0:24:19.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.94,0:24:18.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.78,0:24:20.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop the dancing!{FOTC: YOU HEAR THAT?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.28,0:24:21.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a challenge, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.28,0:24:21.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Iwasawa's replacement?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.90,0:24:22.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what the hell I did before I died!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.24,0:24:23.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make the best team ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.03,0:24:22.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui, nyan <3
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.28,0:24:22.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are we fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.28,0:24:22.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.95,0:24:25.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a punishment game more terrifying than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.57,0:24:25.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your team is not registered.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.36,0:24:28.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That might feel better than anything yet...
